import { toast } from 'react-toastify'
import 'react-toastify/dist/ReactToastify.css'

function toastError() {
  toast.error('Pet não cadastrado !', {
    theme: 'light',
    autoClose: 5000,
    draggable: false,
    closeOnClick: true,
    pauseOnHover: false,
    hideProgressBar: false,
    position: 'top-center',
  })
}
export default toastError
